data.description: This property is strictly for the visionary.  INVESTOR SPECIAL OR OWNER OCCUPANT WITH A VISION FOR WHAT CAN BE! Located in the picturesque Southwest Reno area, this property boasts breathtaking city views that will leave you in awe. While it currently requires some tender loving care, the potential it holds is immense, making it an ideal candidate for a rewarding fix-and-flip project or for someone with a vision to transform it into their dream home. The house features a spacious layout with 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The convenience of a 3-car garage adds an extra layer of functionality, allowing for secure parking and additional storage.  With 2564 sq. ft of living space, there's room to breathe and customize the interiors to suit your preferences. The property's prime location not only offers stunning city views but also ensures proximity to various amenities, making it a promising investment or a charming home for those willing to put in the effort to bring out its full potential. Don't miss the opportunity to turn this property into a gem in the heart of Southwest Reno.
